#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "pyodide.asm.mjs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"The JavaScript half of the main \"binary\". Direct output from the "
"Emscripten compiler. Contains the Emscripten bootstrap code + all JavaScript "
"libraries used by C + the JavaScript/Wasm runtime interop APIs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "pyodide.asm.wasm"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"The WebAssembly half of the main \"binary\". Direct output from the "
"Emscripten compiler. Contains all C library code that is statically linked. "
"Also includes enough of libcxx to support things like exceptions in "
"extension modules that use C++."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "pyodide.js"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"Exports loadPyodide on globalThis. Legacy support for people who can't use "
"es6 modules for whatever reason. Prefer pyodide.mjs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "pyodide.mjs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"A small JS loader shim which exports loadPyodide. It manages downloading the "
"runtime and handling user settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "python_stdlib.zip"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"The Python Standard Library for pyodide. A zip file consisting of the Python "
"Lib folder and the Pyodide Python runtime libraries. Mounted directly into "
"the Pyodide FS and imported using ZipImporter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "package.json"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"Tells node how to use Pyodide, since pyodide-core was primarily intended for "
"use with node."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid "pyodide-lock.json"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../usage/downloading-and-deploying.md:0
msgid ""
"Lockfile for Python packages, used by pyodide.loadPackage and micropip."
"install. Necessary in all cases."
msgstr ""

